From: "Rafael J. Wysocki" <rafael.j.wysocki@intel.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Dec 2021 17:37:10 +0100
Subject: ACPI: Use acpi_fetch_acpi_dev() instead of acpi_bus_get_device()
Patch-mainline: v5.17-rc1
Git-commit: 99ece713773bfa17fdb4ee2a1fb3b7bee82e4b1a
